<!--components/w-swiper/w-swiper.wxml-->
<swiper class="top-swiper" 
        circular 
        autoplay 
        interval="2000" 
        duration="300" 
        indicator-dots 
        indicator-active-color="#ff5777">
  <block wx:for="{{list}}" wx:key="index">
    <swiper-item class="swiper-item">
      <image class="item-image" src="{{item.image}}" mode="widthFix"/>
    </swiper-item>
  </block>
</swiper>
